    - >
      S. Phaneuf & Associates is a full-service excavation contractor, specializing in residential, commercial, and industrial site development for properties across Massachusetts. Our solid reputation was built on hard work, years of outstanding customer service, and on-time project delivery.
    - >
      Beyond digging structural cuts and leveling construction sites, we meticulously handle all subgrade preparation, finish grading, and drainage integrations. We also secure all necessary municipal licenses and engineering permits required to perform the work safely, protecting both our workers and the surrounding environment.
    - >
      A successful construction project always starts with a rock-solid foundation. Our team utilizes a fleet of top-tier, well-maintained heavy equipment to ensure all earthwork operations are completed with extreme precision. From single foundation cuts to complete subdivisions, we deliver professional ground prep engineered to last.
  callout:
